<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really? Thanks!</b></font>

68
00:04:20,504 --> 00:04:21,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...</b></font>

69
00:04:21,834 --> 00:04:23,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...on one condition.</b></font>

70
00:04:23,944 --> 00:04:25,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Condition?</b></font>

71
