81
00:05:32,744 --> 00:05:34,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's that?</b></font>

82
00:05:34,674 --> 00:05:36,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An Eight-Six?</b></font>

83
00:05:43,214 --> 00:05:45,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>These guys are awesome!</i></b></font>

84
00:05:45,854 --> 00:05:47,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>They might be the real deal.</i></b></font>

85
00:05:59,564 --> 00:06:02,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey Ryosuke, get up. We're here.</b></font>

86
00:06:02,534 --> 00:06:04,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please get up, Ryosuke.</b></font>

87
00:06:04,944 --> 00:06:06,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke!</b></font>

88
00:06:07,744 --> 00:06:13,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke has such incredible
concentration on anything he does.</b></font>

89
00:06:13,044 --> 00:06:17,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He hasn't opened his eyes once
since we left Takasaki.</b></font>

90
00:06:17,084 --> 00:06:22,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big brother knows what
works most efficiently.</b></font>

91
00:06:23,794 --> 00:06:27,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry Matsumoto, but please
get me a bottle of cold water.</b></font>

92
00:06:27,094 --> 00:06:28,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

93
00:06:44,244 --> 00:06:45,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's begin.</b></font>

94
00:06:48,514 --> 00:06:52,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello. We're Project D, and we've
come from the Gunma area.</b></font>

95
00:06:52,954 --> 00:06:55,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're called Seven Star Leaf.</b></font>

96
00:06:55,824 --> 00:07:02,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our team mainly runs this course.
You'll be going up against us.</b></font>

97
00:07:02,534 --> 00:07:06,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It will be a pleasure. I believe
you've already been informed,</b></font>

98
00:07:06,604 --> 00:07:09,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but do you agree to let us have
this course tonight for training,</b></font>

99
00:07:09,834 --> 00:07:13,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>with the actual race being tomorrow?</b></font>

100
00:07:13,374 --> 00:07:16,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I heard. That's fine.</b></font>

101
00:07:16,874 --> 00:07:21,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Far as I can see, you've only got
