<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're an expeditionary team.</b></font>

104
00:07:27,324 --> 00:07:31,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We've cut down on the number
of cars to eliminate waste.</b></font>

105
00:07:31,894 --> 00:07:34,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six handles downhill races...</b></font>

106
00:07:34,894 --> 00:07:38,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and the FD handles uphills.</b></font>

107
00:07:38,204 --> 00:07:40,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They are the twin aces of our team.</b></font>

108
00:07:42,304 --> 00:07:45,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Very well, with your
permission we'll now begin.</b></font>

109
00:07:48,244 --> 00:07:51,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're more polite than I expected.</b></font>

110
00:07:51,144 --> 00:07:53,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's sort of a letdown how
friendly they are, huh?</b></font>

111
00:07:55,654 --> 00:07:58,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Racing with just two cars
is unexpected enough,</b></font>

112
00:07:58,224 --> 00:08:04,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but what the heck are those
three minivans? A support team?</b></font>

113
00:08:04,064 --> 00:08:09,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six's underbody
configuration will end up like this.</b></font>

114
00:08:11,564 --> 00:08:14,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>These guys aren't your normal team.</b></font>

115
00:08:14,434 --> 00:08:18,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In a racing team, everyone races, right?</b></font>

116
00:08:18,574 --> 00:08:23,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But having a support crew
tag along for just two cars...</b></font>

117
00:08:23,244 --> 00:08:28,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They may be a team, but they're
more like traveling circuit racers.</b></font>

118
00:08:28,084 --> 00:08:31,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not gonna be fooled
by appearances, Atsuro!</b></font>

119
00:08:31,754 --> 00:08:34,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What can these guys
possibly do in a single night?!</b></font>

120
00:08:34,894 --> 00:08:39,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our team's been active for two years.
At even a moderate guess,</b></font>

121
00:08:39,864 --> 00:08:42,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we've run this a thousand times!</b></font>

122
00:08:42,534 --> 00:08:45,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Support team or not,
it won't make a difference!</b></font>

123
00:08:45,564 --> 00:08:48,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A race is between two drivers, right?!</b></font>

124
00:08:48,434 --> 00:08:52,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In a battle between 1.6-liter cars,
there's no way I'll lose!</b></font>

125
00:08:52,474 --> 00:08:54,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's local pride!</b></font>

126
00:08:54,274 --> 00:08:56,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You think I'm gonna be
beaten by some Eight-Six?</b></font>

127
00:08:58,584 --> 00:09:00,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Understood. This is good.</b></font>

128
00:09:00,444 --> 00:09:02,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Make it so that, as much as possible,</b></font>

129
00:09:02,254 --> 00:09:06,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara will voice his opinions
and be made to think for himself.</b></font>

130
00:09:06,284 --> 00:09:07,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right.</b></font>

131
00:09:07,424 --> 00:09:10,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I believe he can't say
anything of importance yet,</b></font>

132
00:09:10,154 --> 00:09:14,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but what is most crucial now
is that he be made to think.</b></font>

133
00:09:14,264 --> 00:09:15,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Understood.</b></font>

134
00:09:20,804 --> 00:09:22,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Have you watched the video?</b></font>

135
00:09:22,574 --> 00:09:25,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, about 40 times.</b></font>

136
00:09:25,174 --> 00:09:28,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then you should have the course in your head.</b></font>

137
00:09:29,474 --> 00:09:33,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Run the first five times at about 70% speed.</b></font>

138
00:09:33,514 --> 00:09:35,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There will be a slight difference</b></font>

139
00:09:35,654 --> 00:09:39,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>between the course as envisioned
and how it is when actually racing it.</b></font>

140
00:09:39,284 --> 00:09:42,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your first job will be to
adjust for that discrepancy.</b></font>

141
00:09:42,494 --> 00:09:44,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

142
00:09:44,264 --> 00:09:46,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke, you understand as well, yes?</b></font>

143
00:09:46,294 --> 00:09:49,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We don't pick up the pace
till this stage is completed.</b></font>

144
00:09:49,264 --> 00:09:51,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, not to worry.</b></font>

145
00:09:51,804 --> 00:09:54,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Very well. Go!</b></font>

146
00:10:18,564 --> 00:10:24,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm headin' out, too. Once I do
up the tires, I'm good to go!</b></font>

