00:10:35,674 --> 00:10:38,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's probably like Tohru said.</b></font>

148
00:10:41,514 --> 00:10:44,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What can they do in a single night... right?</b></font>

149
00:10:46,384 --> 00:10:49,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's how we've gotta think.</b></font>

150
00:10:49,754 --> 00:10:52,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can ponder all kinds of stuff,</b></font>

151
00:10:52,064 --> 00:10:54,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but in the end,
when racin' out on the course...</b></font>

152
00:10:57,264 --> 00:11:02,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...all you can believe in are your
own driving skills and your car!</b></font>

153
00:11:10,844 --> 00:11:13,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

154
00:11:15,954 --> 00:11:17,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be back.</b></font>

155
00:11:41,244 --> 00:11:43,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much!</b></font>

156
00:11:52,224 --> 00:11:56,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're in a rather good mood, Itsuki.</b></font>

157
00:11:56,094 --> 00:12:01,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That I am, Mr. Iketani!
Because it's almost payday!</b></font>

158
00:12:01,934 --> 00:12:03,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, that's right.</b></font>

159
00:12:03,834 --> 00:12:08,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'll be your first paycheck since
becoming a full-time employee.</b></font>

160
00:12:08,104 --> 00:12:12,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure enough, it's a different
feeling from working part-time!</b></font>

161
00:12:12,174 --> 00:12:15,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It feels like I've become an adult!</b></font>

162
00:12:15,414 --> 00:12:18,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And once you get your pay,
what will you spend it on?</b></font>

163
00:12:18,514 --> 00:12:24,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That should be obvious.
I'm adding a turbo to my Eight-Five!</b></font>

164
00:12:24,854 --> 00:12:26,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To your Eight-Five, huh?</b></font>

165
00:12:26,854 --> 00:12:30,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As it is, my Eight-Five can already...</b></font>

166
00:12:30,154 --> 00:12:31,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Vroom</i>!</b></font>

167
00:12:31,864 --> 00:12:35,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...pull ahead of that S13 of yours no problem!</b></font>

168
00:12:35,434 --> 00:12:39,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've already got an estimate on a loan!</b></font>

169
00:12:40,774 --> 00:12:43,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Little by little, I'm getting closer
to realizing my dream!</b></font>

170
00:12:43,774 --> 00:12:45,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It won't be long now before Akina's Eight-Five</b></font>

171
00:12:45,974 --> 00:12:50,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>becomes known in rumor as
the car of a legendary racer!</b></font>

172
00:12:50,144 --> 00:12:51,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Listen to you!</b></font>

173
00:12:53,214 --> 00:12:58,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanna be like Takumi, tearing
up the mountain pass in style!</b></font>

174
00:13:00,324 --> 00:13:05,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Speaking of, I wonder what
Takumi's doing right now...</b></font>

175
00:13:14,064 --> 00:13:16,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Shibukawa Station North</b></font>

176
00:13:14,064 --> 00:13:16,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Audible Traffic Signal"</b></font>

177
00:13:29,914 --> 00:13:34,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's something I've been
thinking about since last fall...</b></font>

178
00:13:34,324 --> 00:13:37,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is my dream?</b></font>

179
00:13:39,264 --> 00:13:44,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought about it all through
the winter, and I finally realized it.</b></font>

180
00:13:44,334 --> 00:13:49,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I like to ride cars, and I want
to be faster than anyone else...</b></font>

181
00:13:51,244 --> 00:13:54,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why I'm going to join Ryosuke's team.</b></font>

182
00:14:04,454 --> 00:14:06,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's definitely...</b></font>

183
00:14:09,194 --> 00:14:12,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...see each other again, okay?</b></font>

184
00:14:14,024 --> 00:14:17,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Shibukawa Station"</b></font>

185
00:14:16,264 --> 00:14:18,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara.</b></font>

186
00:14:19,604 --> 00:14:22,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara!</b></font>

187
00:14:22,434 --> 00:14:23,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sir?</b></font>

188
00:14:23,804 --> 00:14:28,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Spacing out as always.
You're done for today now, right?</b></font>

189
00:14:28,774 --> 00:14:31,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. I had the early shift, so...</b></font>

190
00:14:31,444 --> 00:14:34,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Going on a date or something?</b></font>

191
00:14:34,084 --> 00:14:36,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, not really.</b></font>

192
00:14:36,654 --> 00:14:40,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're not, huh? For a youngster
like you, that's just depressing!</b></font>

193
00:14:49,434 --> 00:14:50,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Scary...</b></font>

194
00:14:50,764 --> 00:14:53,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There are no covers on the sides!</b></font>

195
00:14:53,064 --> 00:14:55,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard about this from Ryosuke,</b></font>

196
00:14:55,434 --> 00:14:58,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but this is the first time I've seen one so deep.</b></font>

197
00:14:58,604 --> 00:15:04,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The roads in the Gunma area
generally have concrete covers.</b></font>

198
00:15:04,144 --> 00:15:06,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We ran it at night yesterday,
so it didn't stand out,</b></font>

199
00:15:06,984 --> 00:15:09,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but if we fell into that thing at full speed,</b></font>

200
00:15:09,184 --> 00:15:12,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>make no mistake,
our undersides would be toast.</b></font>

201
00:15:12,624 --> 00:15:18,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Actually, Ryosuke said
something about this yesterday.</b></font>

202
00:15:18,694 --> 00:15:21,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That how we tackle this ditch</b></font>

203
00:15:21,434 --> 00:15:25,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>would decide whether we win or lose.</b></font>

204
00:15:25,634 --> 00:15:27,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even saying something like that...</b></font>

205
00:15:27,164 --> 00:15:30,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe he just meant,
make sure you don't fall in.</b></font>

206
00:15:34,814 --> 00:15:36,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway...</b></font>

207
00:15:36,014 --> 00:15:38,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A lot of the time, we don't get
what Ryosuke's thinking</b></font>

208
00:15:38,784 --> 00:15:44,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>right up till the very end. However...</b></font>

209
00:15:44,884 --> 00:15:50,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In the end, it always turns
out the way Ryosuke said.</b></font>

210
00:15:50,024 --> 00:15:52,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can believe him.</b></font>

211
00:15:55,794 --> 00:16:00,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A 1600 B6 bored up to 1800...</b></font>

212
00:16:00,504 --> 00:16:04,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An installed high-comp piston,
raising the compression ratio,</b></font>

213
00:16:04,004 --> 00:16:07,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>a lowered flywheel weight
to increase response,</b></font>

214
00:16:07,914 --> 00:16:10,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and finished off with four
throttle body sports injection...</b></font>

215
00:16:10,874 --> 00:16:13,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Too awesome.</b></font>

216
00:16:13,014 --> 00:16:16,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Combined with your driving technique,</b></font>

217
00:16:16,254 --> 00:16:20,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>this is the ultimate downhill B6, I'd say.</b></font>

218
00:16:20,184 --> 00:16:24,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With this, there's no way I could lose! For sure!</b></font>

219
00:16:30,234 --> 00:16:33,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Beware of Brush Fires"</b></font>

220
00:16:33,734 --> 00:16:37,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Souvenirs"</b></font>

221
00:16:41,174 --> 00:16:45,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well then, Bunta, you're still
making Takumi do the deliveries?</b></font>

222
00:16:45,684 --> 00:16:48,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. Nothin's changed from before.</b></font>

223
00:16:48,584 --> 00:16:52,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You say that, but he's become
an upstanding young man.</b></font>

224
00:16:52,224 --> 00:16:54,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He works afternoons now, right?</b></font>

225
00:16:54,524 --> 00:16:57,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He doesn't complain about it or nothin', either.</b></font>

226
00:16:57,694 --> 00:17:00,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's doin' an even better job than before.</b></font>

227
00:17:03,234 --> 00:17:08,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That "Project D" team looks like
it's been good motivation for him.</b></font>

228
00:17:08,534 --> 00:17:11,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. He says they're unbeatable.</b></font>

229
00:17:11,274 --> 00:17:14,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Apparently they're making
new records left and right.</b></font>

230
00:17:14,274 --> 00:17:19,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, for now. But before long...</b></font>

231
00:17:22,114 --> 00:17:24,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...they'll lose.</b></font>

232
00:17:28,894 --> 00:17:31,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's about to start! My heart's pounding.</b></font>

233
00:17:31,494 --> 00:17:34,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How awesome is Project D gonna be?!</b></font>

234
00:17:34,994 --> 00:17:38,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In any case, Seven Star Leaf
is gonna take the downhill.</b></font>

235
00:17:38,804 --> 00:17:43,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way that Tohru Suetsugu
will lose to some out-of-towner!</b></font>

236
00:17:39,504 --> 00:17:47,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Beware of Brush Fires"</b></font>

237
00:17:43,904 --> 00:17:45,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's goin' up against an Eight-Six, right?</b></font>

238
00:17:45,804 --> 00:17:50,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That FD is a powerful machine,
but an Eight-Six is just so old!</b></font>

239
00:17:52,114 --> 00:17:56,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At their request, we'll be
doing the downhill first.</b></font>

240
00:17:56,114 --> 00:17:58,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rather than a simultaneous start,</b></font>

241
00:17:58,124 --> 00:18:01,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>one driver will go first
with the other following.</b></font>

242
00:18:01,354 --> 00:18:03,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They'll go in front on the first race.</b></font>

243
00:18:03,454 --> 00:18:08,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think you realize that if we
lose the first race, it's over.</b></font>

244
00:18:10,464 --> 00:18:11,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's good!</b></font>

245
00:18:11,964 --> 00:18:14,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can start at any time.</b></font>

246
00:18:18,474 --> 00:18:21,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It may be an Eight-Six, but don't
let your guard down, Tohru.</b></font>

247
00:18:21,374 --> 00:18:24,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's definitely not an ordinary Eight-Six.</b></font>

248
00:18:24,344 --> 00:18:26,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know.</b></font>

249
00:18:26,684 --> 00:18:29,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't care what kind of car the other guy has!</b></font>

250
00:18:29,854 --> 00:18:34,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right now, I'm gonna do
the best racing that I can!</b></font>

251
00:18:34,184 --> 00:18:35,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tohru!</b></font>

252
00:18:35,824 --> 00:18:38,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shinichi, hold your hand out.</b></font>

253
00:18:42,794 --> 00:18:44,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You get it, right?</b></font>

254
00:18:44,834 --> 00:18:46,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm shaking.</b></font>

255
00:18:46,504 --> 00:18:49,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's scary! The truth is, it's so
scary that I've got the jitters</b></font>

256
00:18:49,834 --> 00:18:53,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and just wanna run away from here!</b></font>

257
00:18:53,074 --> 00:18:58,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But at the same time, I'm happy.
I'm so happy I can't take it!</b></font>

258
00:18:58,914 --> 00:19:00,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you know why?</b></font>

259
00:19:02,054 --> 00:19:07,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm grateful to Project D.
You can be a racer for a long time</b></font>

260
00:19:07,724 --> 00:19:11,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and almost never get to race
with this kinda incredible tension.</b></font>

261
00:19:11,224 --> 00:19:17,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To me, today's race is the chance
of a lifetime to show my stuff!</b></font>

262
00:19:17,434 --> 00:19:20,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As a representative of Seven Star Leaf,</b></font>

263
00:19:20,934 --> 00:19:25,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll make damn sure I run a
good race, with no regrets!</b></font>

264
00:19:25,844 --> 00:19:28,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the spirit, Tohru.</b></font>

265
00:19:28,274 --> 00:19:32,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right then, whaddya say
we get this thing started?!</b></font>

266
00:19:39,524 --> 00:19:42,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tohru Suetsugu. A pleasure.</b></font>

267
00:19:42,594 --> 00:19:44,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm Takumi Fujiwara.</b></font>

268
00:19:46,024 --> 00:19:49,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Wh-What is this feeling?!</i></b></font>

269
00:19:53,304 --> 00:19:57,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've never felt this way before!</i></b></font>

270
00:19:57,534 --> 00:20:01,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm stunned... I'm so shocked I can't stand it!</i></b></font>

271
00:20:06,144 --> 00:20:10,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Protect me... Naho!</i></b></font>

272
00:20:39,244 --> 00:20:42,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Tohru! I was so blown away by</i>
<i>Tohru's downhill corner entry</i></b></font>

273
00:20:42,954 --> 00:20:49,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>that I joined this team. He's a</i>
<i>do-or-die kamikaze downhiller!</i></b></font>

274
00:20:49,194 --> 00:20:52,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's not a person out there who</i>
<i>can keep up with Tohru's downhill!</i></b></font>

275
00:20:56,834 --> 00:21:00,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's no way he's gonna lose</i>
<i>to some out-of-town Eight-Six!</i></b></font>

276
00:21:06,704 --> 00:21:11,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Going first was the right choice for me.</i></b></font>

277
00:21:11,114 --> 00:21:15,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If your rhythm gets thrown off,</i>
<i>the downhill can be deadly!</i></b></font>

278
00:21:23,524 --> 00:21:25,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Be relaxed... Rather than winning or losing,</i></b></font>

279
00:21:25,994 --> 00:21:29,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>what's most important is that</i>
<i>you give everything you've got.</i></b></font>

280
00:21:37,734 --> 00:21:43,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Compared to the Eight-Six,
the Roadster is even more compact,</b></font>

281
00:21:43,014 --> 00:21:44,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>its small size and weight</b></font>

282
00:21:44,884 --> 00:21:47,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>allowing for the nimble footwork
that is its greatest weapon!</b></font>

283
00:21:51,214 --> 00:21:55,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And the downhill of its
driver Tohru Suetsugu will,</b></font>

284
00:21:55,094 --> 00:21:59,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>as I see it, bet everything
on high-speed corner entry.</b></font>

285
00:21:59,494 --> 00:22:02,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It is an unrefined style.</b></font>

286
00:22:02,394 --> 00:22:06,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Each and every corner will
be taken with an inertia drift.</b></font>

287
00:22:11,444 --> 00:22:13,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It is a driving style in which everything begins</b></font>

288
00:22:13,174 --> 00:22:18,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>when cornering speed has been
taken almost as high as it can.</b></font>

289
00:22:18,344 --> 00:22:20,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It could perhaps even be said
that his driving technique</b></font>

290
00:22:20,784 --> 00:22:24,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>was cultivated through the Roadster,
a car that lacks power.</b></font>

291
00:22:24,214 --> 00:22:26,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Meaning that he and Fujiwara...</b></font>

292
00:22:26,124 --> 00:22:28,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. His is much like the relationship</b></font>

293
00:22:28,854 --> 00:22:31,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>between Fujiwara and the Eight-Six.</b></font>

294
00:22:34,694 --> 00:22:37,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With just one exception.</b></font>

295
00:22:37,794 --> 00:22:40,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whoa! Awesome!</b></font>

